were headquartered at Cu Chi, and I spent most of my

01:01.213 --> 01:04.918
time The first half of the year in the field with the 
Charlie Company out near Hard Spot, Harris,

01:05.337 --> 01:17.118
Firebase, Jackson, near the Cambodian border. 
