01:17.138 --> 01:28.459
spent on top of the mountains that we bought then, 
the Black Virgin just outside of Tainan, inside

01:17.138 --> 01:28.459
Tainan Province. And that's significant because 
it was the only elevation, the only relief spot in

01:29.198 --> 01:42.545
the area, in that whole South Vietnam area. And so 
it was used by strategic communications. And

01:48.858 --> 02:07.442
messages that were broadcast from the Pentagon by 
radio across Europe and retransmitted down

01:48.858 --> 02:07.442
through Turkey came in to the mountains because 
the rest of the area, as I said, was flat. And it was

02:08.263 --> 02:10.305
kind of the key communication point. They were 
relayed through a different series of steps to us,

02:10.325 --> 02:18.696
